before they came in.

00:38:43.400 --> 00:38:46.560
It was in this context that
Abu Talal Al-Qasimi arrived,

00:38:46.760 --> 00:38:50.640
an Egyptian of whom the Danish
authorities should have been wary.

00:38:53.640 --> 00:38:58.000
His story is very closely linked
to one of the most violent pages

00:38:58.200 --> 00:39:00.840
of Islamist terror in the 1980s.

00:39:06.320 --> 00:39:10.800
CAIRO, EGYPT
6 OCTOBER 1981

00:39:11.000 --> 00:39:13.720
It should have been a simple
military parade.

00:39:32.200 --> 00:39:36.400
In the official box, Anwar el-Sadat,
the Egyptian president,

00:39:36.720 --> 00:39:39.440
