the Danish Muslim community.

00:42:08.440 --> 00:42:12.520
He made these fear speeches
every Saturday at the mosque

00:42:12.720 --> 00:42:14.400
where he called for jihad,

00:42:14.720 --> 00:42:19.200
so he kind of had the influence,
