00:42:19.520 --> 00:42:23.160
to the course of jihadism
in Denmark,

00:42:23.360 --> 00:42:27.560
building the stones for generations
to come afterwards.

00:42:31.920 --> 00:42:36.880
This little radical group even got
his former cell companion,

00:42:37.080 --> 00:42:40.800
the blind sheikh Abdel Rahman,
to come on a tour of Denmark.

00:42:45.760 --> 00:42:48.000
The blind sheikh
was really a rock star.

00:42:48.200 --> 00:42:52.840
People came from all over
the country to greet him.

00:42:53.160 --> 00:42:55.960
It was only afterwards that

00:42:56.160 --> 00:43:00.240
