00:49:55.480 --> 00:49:56.960
Down, down USA!

00:49:57.160 --> 00:49:58.720
Down, down USA!

00:49:58.920 --> 00:50:00.480
USA, you will pay!

00:50:00.680 --> 00:50:02.480
USA, you will pay!

